      </div>

      <div class="bg-lime-50 border-[3px] border-lime-200 p-6 mb-6">
        <p class="font-black text-lime-900 text-lg mb-4">THE FIX (Week 1: Samples + Results Front-and-Center)</p>
        <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">Day 1-2: Built Webflow site with writing samples gallery on homepage (scrollable samples: B2B SaaS blog posts, email sequences, whitepapers, case studies), each sample with client results visible ("300% traffic increase, 6 months," "47% email open rate, 12% conversion"), added "Our Work" page with filterable portfolio by industry (SaaS, Fintech, Healthcare, E-commerce), service pages with specific offerings ("B2B SaaS Blog Writing: 4 posts/month, SEO-optimized, published under your name," "Product Launch Content: Landing page, email sequence, social posts"), team bios with expertise ("Sarah Chen: 8 years SaaS content, former HubSpot writer"), lead capture form ("Get Content Samples + Proposal in 24 hours"). Cost: $2,400 (Webflow setup $1,800, content migration $600). Launch: November 12, 2024.</p>
